text.tspan: SS0[0-8] SPI Slave Select lines of SPI bus 0 (the [] is the motor ID)
MOSI[0-2] SPI Motor Control Master Out Slave In lines
MISO[0-2] SPI Motor Control Master In Slave Out
SCK[0-2] SPI Motor Control clock lines
SCL[0-4]/SDA[0-4] I2C clock/data line for four separate i2c cores
SS1[9-12] SPI Slave Select lines of SPI bus 1 (the [] is the motor ID)
SS2[13-15] SPI Slave Select lines of SPI bus 2 (the [] is the motor ID)
SS3[0-5] SPI Slave Select lines of SPI bus 3
MOSI[0-2] SPI Sensor Master Out Slave In lines
MISO[0-2] SPI Sensor Master In Slave Out
SS4[0-5] SPI Slave Select lines of SPI bus 4
